
Template: alba/reconfigure-webserver
Type: multiselect
Choices: apache2, lighttpd
Default: apache2
Description: Which web server would you like to reconfigure automatically?
 Alba can run on any web server that PHP5 does, but this automatic
 configuration process only supports Apache2 and Lighttpd.

